{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The Institutional Review Board of NYU Grossman School of Medicine approved all experimental procedures.",
    "After consulting with the clinical-care provider, a research team member obtained written and oral consent from each participant.",
    "Each participant performed five tasks 47 to produce target words in response to auditory or visual stimuli.",
    "The tasks were auditory repetition (AR, repeating auditory words), auditory naming (AN, naming a word based on an auditory definition), sentence completion (SC, completing the last word of an auditory sentence), visual reading (VR, reading aloud written words) and picture naming (PN, naming a word based on a colour drawing).",
    "For each task, we used the exact 50 target words with different stimulus modalities (auditory, visual and so on)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Each participant performed five tasks 47 to produce target words in response to auditory or visual stimuli."
  ]
}